---
title: American Pulled Beef & Black Bean Chilli with Avocado & Homemade Tortilla Chips
description: Gather round everybody – it’s chilli night! We're giving it a taste of the USA with our Louisiana spice blend and have included a
solid array of fillings like pulled beef, black beans and avocado so you can feel good about digging into this flavourful feast.

* Our pulled beef is gently cooked while vacuum-sealed (or sous vide as the French say). The meat may look pale, but it's packed with flavour and moisture!*

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
